6.21	Clarkia	Clarkia	Clarkia is a genus within the flowering plant family Onagraceae. Over 40 species are currently classified in Clarkia; almost all are native to western North America, though one species is native to South America.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b1/Clarkia_amoena.jpg/240px-Clarkia_amoena.jpg
